This pattern library wraps upstream work — Anthropic's Model Context Protocol
specification, the first-party MCP servers (Linear, GitHub, and others), and
the mcp-remote HTTP-to-stdio bridge. It builds on prior framing of agent
infrastructure by Nate B. Jones, and on contributions to the OpenClaw / OB1
ecosystem by Alan Shurafa. See README.md for full credit.
